<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13050</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们和妈妈看着黑黑的房子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25376</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“窗户怎么关着？我让维尼夫人打开的。”妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25376</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28865</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“维尼夫人是谁？”鲍比问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28865</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34238</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是我请来帮我们打扫卫生和做晚餐的阿姨。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34238</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37192</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们走到房子后面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37192</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41058</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马车嘎吱嘎吱地跟着他们，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41058</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43461</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>也停在了后门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43461</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45958</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们敲了敲门，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45958</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但没人回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51930</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>车夫说维尼夫人可能已经回家了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51930</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55482</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为火车到得太晚了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55482</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60358</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是钥匙在她那里！”妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60359</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊，不过我猜她一定会把钥匙放在门口的台阶下面。”车夫说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68917</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里人都是这样的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76978</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把马车上的灯笼拿下来，弯下腰。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76977</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78928</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真的在这儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78928</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81579</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他拿钥匙打开了门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81578</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85504</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>车夫放下灯笼，点亮蜡烛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89555</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>厨房很大，地面是石头铺的 。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89555</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91311</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>桌子在中间，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91311</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96793</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>椅子、罐子、锅和碗到处都是。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96793</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100841</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>壁炉里没有火，只有灰。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100841</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105779</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然墙里传来沙沙的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105779</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110512</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！什么声音？”女孩儿们大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110512</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114107</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“只是老鼠而已。”车夫说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114107</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116208</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他关上门走了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116208</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120366</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然一阵风把蜡烛吹灭了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120366</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123377</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“天呐！”菲利斯说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123377</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125543</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不想住在这里！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125543</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129122</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把一把椅子推倒了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“只是老鼠而已！”彼得在黑暗中说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“多好玩儿呀！”妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她摸到了火柴，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142257</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“肯定是一群可爱的小老鼠！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142257</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144213</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她擦亮火柴，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144213</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147456</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家互相看着对方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147456</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好了。”妈妈说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150115</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们不是经常希望发生点儿什么事吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156372</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在事情已经发生了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156372</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159797</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们就把它当作是一次冒险吧！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159797</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165030</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>走，我们去尝尝维尼夫人给我们准备的晚餐吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165030</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168137</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>餐厅在厨房旁边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168137</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170784</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>厨房是白色的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是餐厅从地板到天花板，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174116</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177998</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>整个都是用深色的木材做的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177998</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184050</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>餐厅里有桌子和椅子，但是没有晚餐。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184050</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187962</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们去看看其他房间吧。”妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187962</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190364</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们看了一圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190364</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196056</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个房间都有家具和箱子，但没有吃的东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196056</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198622</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就连储存食物的房间里，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198622</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203255</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>也只有一个生锈的蛋糕烤盘 。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203255</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206906</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真是个糟糕的女人！”妈妈说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206906</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她拿了钱，却不给我们吃的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210037</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215110</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们没有晚餐吃了。”菲利斯伤心地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215110</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219255</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别担心，我们有吃的。”妈妈说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219255</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225140</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“ 我们带来的箱子中有一个里面有一些吃的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225140</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227112</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们都很累，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227112</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232445</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是因为晚餐很特别，他们又变得开心起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232445</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>晚餐有饼干、沙丁鱼、葡萄干和果酱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238136</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242069</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>晚餐后，他们铺好床。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242069</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“晚安，孩子们。”妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245450</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248528</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我保证这里没有老鼠！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248528</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253509</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我会开着门，万一发现了老鼠，你们可以大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253509</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256388</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我会过来把老鼠赶走！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261174</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比、彼得和菲利斯不相信她的话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261174</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269313</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们点着蜡烛，度过了新家的第一个晚上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>